lead_paragraph: Adam Nemec showed he could provide the scoring threat Slovakia need in their European Championship debut by netting two goals to secure a 3-1 win over Georgia on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Nemec Shines as Slovakia Beat Georgia in Euro Warm-Up
